     Space group Fd-3m   (group number 227).
     The origin coincides with the ITA tables (origin choice 1).

     To shift to origin choice 2 subtract to all coordinates:
                 (cryst. coord.)                  (cart. coord.)
       -0.1250000  -0.1250000  -0.1250000     0.1250000  -0.1250000  -0.1250000

     The Laue class is O_h (m-3m) 

